{"tid":1284154,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［運動救港］聽講運動可以防止自殺","createTime":"2019-07-04T04:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T05:22:06.000Z","uid":261982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d94909fe58e095932311197d89440619f1b7e649","tid":1284154,"uid":261982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:57:24.000Z","msg":"運動時大腦會產生內啡呔<br />\n咁就會令人有開心/抵抗抑鬱<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<br />\n（未fact chaeck)<br />\n<br />\n就算唔得<br />\n記得拉埋你個frd去跑下步<br />\n有人陪 點都會開心啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算上面都唔得<br />\n最少下次黎搬物資都可以輕鬆啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議各大公海推廣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細路 唔好灰，未來仲要靠你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d47b26169764ca9ae6ddb6eb59cd51c6f66181","tid":1284154,"uid":261982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e018b6c7ac4cbc86a8131c27f1b3f635093345e","tid":1284154,"uid":261982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:59:08.000Z","msg":"我有野講啊！！！<br />\n唔好灰心啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58821d6b430fa70b9ca308acb89a404972968543","tid":1284154,"uid":261982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2